ASSETS LICENSE (placeholder)

This file covers the 3D body assets only. The application code is covered by
the MIT license in LICENSE.

The visual body meshes for WhereItHurts are planned to be exported from
MakeHuman (www.makehumancommunity.org), whose generated meshes are CC0 —
no attribution or share-alike obligation applies. In that case this file
reduces to a courtesy provenance note, to be finalized when the exports are
integrated.

If the fallback path is taken instead (deriving from BodyParts3D, Z-Anatomy,
or Open3DModel, which are CC BY-SA), the derived asset will be distributed
under CC BY-SA with full attribution, and this file will carry the final
attribution text.

Until real assets land, the app ships generated placeholder primitive meshes
that are original to this repository and carry no third-party license
obligations (see scripts/make-placeholder-body.mjs).
